profile:
Wash-Pro Pressure Washing offers a wide variety of residential and commercial pressure washing services including:

House Washing

Roof Washing

Concrete Cleaning

Rust Stain Removal

Exterior Building Washing

and more!

We specialize in low pressure soft washing, meaning we use our low pressure, soft wash process on every home, roof, and building we wash. We serve all of Essex County including Windsor, Tecumseh, Lakeshore, Belle River, The Town Of Essex, Lasalle, Amherstburg, Leamington, and everywhere in between.
